        </div>
    </div>

    <section id="our-commitment" class="commitment-section">
        <div class="commitment-container">
            <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
            <div class="commitment-grid">
                <div class="commitment-item">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i>
                    <h3>Transparency</h3>
                    <p>We ensure a transparent process for all our users, providing clear and honest information at every step.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="commitment-item">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-gears"></i>
                    <h3>Efficiency</h3>
                    <p>Our platform is designed to facilitate quick and effective connections between startups and investors.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="commitment-item">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-headset"></i>
                    <h3>Support</h3>
                    <p>We provide continuous support to our users, helping them navigate the complexities of the investment landscape.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="commitment-item">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-handshake"></i>
                    <h3>Collaboration</h3>
                    <p>We foster a collaborative environment where startups and investors can thrive together.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="fees-and-payments" class="fees-section">
        <div class="fees-container">
           
            <h2>Fees and Payments</h2>
            <div class="fees-cards">
                <div class="fees-card">
                    <div class="fees-icon-container">
                        <i class="fas fa-bullhorn fees-icon"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fees-content">
                        <h3>Showcase Fee</h3>
                        <p>We charge a fee for showcasing your startup on our platform, ensuring maximum visibility to potential investors.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="fees-card">
                    <div class="fees-icon-container">
                        <i class="fas fa-percentage fees-icon"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fees-content">
                        <h3>Transaction Fee</h3>
                        <p>We take a 1% fee on every investment transaction to sustain our platform and continue providing top-notch services.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="fees-card">
                    <div class="fees-icon-container">
                        <i class="fas fa-crown fees-icon"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fees-content">
                        <h3>Premium Services</h3>
                        <p>Access to our financial advisor is a premium feature. Users can subscribe to this service for expert guidance on investments.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
